'''''Intego ya Assassin''''' ni film yo mu 1977 iyobowe na Peter Collinson ikinwamo na Anthony Quinn na John Phillip Law . yafatiwe amashusho muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]] mu 1976 ikitwa '''''Tigers Don't Cry''''' ariko ntabwo yashyizwe ahagaragara muri [[Amerika]] imyaka hafi icyenda. andi mazina  arimo ''African Rage'', ''The Long Shot'', and ''Fatal Assassin''..  Ukurikije igitabo cya  Jon Burmeister cyitwa ''Running Scared''. 

