== Umugambi ==
Filime yakiniwe mubitaro byo muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika]] yepfo. Anthony Quinn wamenyekanye cyane akina nk'umuforomo w'umugabo, Hobday, washinzwe kwita kuri perezida w’amahanga (Simon Sabela). Hamwe n’iterabwoba ryinshi ryangiza ubuzima bwe, umuyobozi arinzwe cyane kumasaha. Hobday abasha gushimuta umurwayi we ku nyungu z'umuntu ku giti cye, atazi ko sniper yahawe akazi agerageza guhitana ubuzima bw'umuyobozi w’amahanga igihe yari afunzwe na Hobday. Ibi biganisha kumurongo wamatsiko y'imigambi iganisha kumiterere yikirere hamwe n'imodoka ya kabili kumusozi muremure.
